en-US.title: Peach Clinics - Prahran
en-US.description: Located at Prahran Victoria, Peach Clinics provides electrolysis hair removal services. The clinic aims to provide a comfortable and respectful environment, and is inclusive to individuals of all identities including the transgender community, ensuring accessible and dedicated care for transmasculine, transfeminine, and non-binary individuals.

address: Shop 1/161 Greville St, Prahran VIC 3181, Australia
